attributes.Long form description: The student will work with assembling a piece of furniture by first inspecting the position that the furniture will start, and then he assembles the first leg, continues assembling the second leg, and then the third leg and finishes with the fourth leg. He continues securing the screws of the furniture, starts assembling the first leg to the top of the furniture and continues assembling the fourth leg. To finish, he screws each of the screws of the furniture to be secured and finishes the video.

attributes.Transcription: We'll now assemble the small shelf from Ikea.
So please go ahead and assemble it.
